name: Red Cup
description: Today, I want softness in our world, tranquility, quiet, peaceful. Say all that with a mouthful of rocks. Let's just have a good time. Dont think theres anybody that does'nt like mountains. Well, maybe there is. We dont know where it goes. The other thing that is so fantastic about painting is that it teaches you to see. It's easy to add more color, but it's a son of a gun to take it away.

name: Cool Cup
description: The more that you practice, the more you're able to visualize things. It does'nt take much, but you have to devote that time. Create that little fuzzy look. It's always trying to go somewhere that it can be level. Sort of mix it up. Enough of that. Have to have dark in order to show light.

name: Dotted Cup
description: You've got to have a little sadness once in awhile to let you know when the good times come. Just let them fall right out of your brush. It's very hard to see your painting when you're right up against it. Sometimes it's fun to play little games in your mountains. It takes very little color. They are restricted only by your imagination. You make the big decisions where all these things live in your world.

name: Blue Cup
description: And that easy, we've got a happy mountain. Mountains are so simple that they're hard! It's very easy to make a sky darker, but it's a son of a gun to make it lighter. Today, I want softness in our world... tranquility, quiet, peaceful. Only takes a minute. ...two hairs and some air... Do a cabin-ectomy.

name: Splatter Cup
description: Wiggle it, then sharpen it. Get a nice, even distribution of paint all through the bristles. You're limited only by your imagination. Let it sort of bounce around and play. You didnt know you had so much power, did you? You can create any illusion that you can conceive in your mind. All you do is just go back with it.

name: Pink Cup
description: It's just a game of angles. They just sort of bounce around and have fun up there. You can create any illusion that you can conceive in your mind. When the birds take over, I'll have friends! It's a fantastic day here, and I hope it is wherever you're at. That simple, that easy! You dont have to work at it hardly at all.

name: Marble Cup
description: You'll be amazed at what you can do if you'll just try. Have to have dark in order to show light. Wherever you think they should be, then thats exactly where they should be. It helps, when you're doing these kinds of things, make up little stories in your mind. Absolutely no limits! Painting offers freedom. Sort of mix it up.

name: Leaf Cup
description: We'll start playing a little bit. All we do is just sorta have an idea in our mind, and we just sorta let it happen. A very, very small amount. Everybody will see nature through different eyes It's just a game of angles. I'll show you exactly the kind of messes we get into sometimes. This is where you take out all your frustrations and all your hostilities, and just have a good time.

name: Black Cup
description: See how easy that is? You can just go on and on and on. Just let it sorta dance around in the sky. Pull from the outside in. Just gonna start any 'ol where. Soft as a meadow. Let's take the almighty brush here

name: Gradient Cup
description: Take right off today! That little painter man is so cute! Wiggle it, then sharpen it. Tongue got over my teeth there and I couldnt see what I was saying. A half a hair and some air. We dont know where that goes. Looks like theres a storm coming already.
